nd the broader region.” I'll craft this in Dutch and include the date, which is today, April 16, 2026. I'll say, \"Here are the most recent points (latest reports up to April 16, 2026)\" and provide the list. No further web calls are necessary."}]},{"id":"msg_04c8e0b6f86052560169e0883fa27481a3bf14854c9b644f9e","type":"message","status":"completed","content":[{"type":"output_text","annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","end_index":465,"start_index":390,"title":"Pakistani army chief visits Tehran in bid to broker renewed talks between US and Iran | AP News","url":"https://apnews.com/article/297a8d2bb94add26e503a4ef3a5d1151"},{"type":"url_citation","end_index":911,"start_index":828,"title":"U.S. and Iran inch toward framework deal to end war, U.S. officials say","url":"https://www.axios.com/2026/04/15/iran-war-negotiations-deal-pakistan"},{"type":"url_citation","end_index":1301,"start_index":1226,"title":"Trump administration pivots to economic warfare on Iran | AP News","url":"https://apnews.com/article/f45619d7ea3050bd4b1cdd9c3881ca2b"},{"type":"url_citation","end_index":1598,"start_index":1523,"title":"Senate Republicans again reject effort to halt Iran war | AP News","url":"https://apnews.com/article/8a47ef050f05d49677c5f4cf2f6bfbd4"},{"type":"url_citation","end_index":1879,"start_index":1804,"title":"Pakistani army chief visits Tehran in bid to broker renewed talks between US and Iran | AP News","url":"https://apnews.com/article/297a8d2bb94add26e503a4ef3a5d1151"},{"type":"url_citation","end_index":2099,"start_index":2024,"title":"FIFA president Infantino says Iran will participate in World Cup 'for sure' | AP News","url":"https://apnews.com/article/4854d5588b7985d2fb0a6c638f8e42b5"}],"logprobs":[],"text":"Hier is **laatste nieuws (t/m 16 april 2026)** over de **oorlog/conflict rond Iran** (in de berichtgeving vooral het **VS–Iran-conflict**, met bredere regionale impact):\n\n- **Nieuwe diplomatieke poging (VS–Iran) via Pakistan en Iran**\n  - De **legerchef van Pakistan** gaat naar **Teheran** om hernieuwde gesprekken te faciliteren en de spanningen te temperen, na bijna zeven weken oorlog. ([apnews.com](https://apnews.com/article/297a8d2bb94add26e503a4ef3a5d1151))\n\n- **Onderhandelingen richting een “framework deal”**\n  - VS en Iran zouden **richting een kaderafspraak** gaan om de oorlog te beëindigen, met bemiddeling door o.a. Pakistan (en ook Egyptische/Turkse bemiddelaars genoemd).\n  - Er wordt gemeld dat het **staakt-het-vuren op 21 april 2026** afloopt, en dat men probeert vóór/rond die datum vooruitgang te boeken. ([axios.com](https://www.axios.com/2026/04/15/iran-war-negotiations-deal-pakistan))\n\n- **Mogelijke verschuiving naar “economische oorlogsvoering” als het niet lukt**\n  - De VS bereidt, als er geen deal komt of geen verlenging volgt, een **meer economisch gerichte campagne** voor (o.a. **secundaire sancties** en druk op financiële instellingen), “als financieel equivalent” van de bombardementen. ([apnews.com](https://apnews.com/article/f45619d7ea3050bd4b1cdd9c3881ca2b))\n\n- **Amerikaans politiek debat: Senaat stemt tegen stopzetten van de oorlog**\n  - De Senaat (met Republikeinse meerderheid) wijst een poging af om de oorlog te stoppen; er wordt gemeld dat het om een **47–52 stem** ging. ([apnews.com](https://apnews.com/article/8a47ef050f05d49677c5f4cf2f6bfbd4))\n\n- **Wat staat er inzet in diplomatieke “sticking points”?**\n  - In dezelfde berichtgeving komen o.a. terug: **Iran’s nucleair programma**, de **Straat van Hormuz**, en **compensatie voor oorlogsschade**. ([apnews.com](https://apnews.com/article/297a8d2bb94add26e503a4ef3a5d1151))\n\n- **Opvallend nevenbericht (sport)**\n  - FIFA-voorzitter **Infantino** zegt dat **Iran “voor zeker”** deelneemt aan het WK, ondanks de oorlog. ([apnews.com](https://apnews.com/article/4854d5588b7985d2fb0a6c638f8e42b5))\n\nWil je dat ik dit toespits op **(1) gevechten/aanvallen**, **(2) onderhandelingen & staakt-het-vuren**, of **(3) binnenlandse situatie in Iran**?"}],"phase":"final_answer","role":"assistant"}],"parallel_tool_calls":true,"presence_penalty":0.0,"previous_response_id":null,"prompt_cache_key":null,"prompt_cache_retention":null,"reasoning":{"effort":"medium","summary":"detailed"},"safety_identifier":null,"service_tier":"default","store":false,"temperature":1.0,"text":{"format":{"type":"text"},"verbosity":"medium"},"tool_choice":"auto","tools":[{"type":"web_search","search_context_size":"low","user_location":{"type":"approximate","city":null,"country":"US","region":null,"timezone":null}}],"top_logprobs":0,"top_p":0.98,"truncation":"auto","usage":{"input_tokens":21561,"input_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":0},"output_tokens":1761,"output_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":1171},"total_tokens":23322},"user":null,"metadata":{}},"sequence_number":385}

